## Product Scope Translation of BUILD_GUIDE (Decision-Complete)
1. **Role policy**
   | Role | Account creation rule |
   |---|---|
   | Client | Self-signup via Auth0 email/social |
   | Reader | Public application form allowed; platform profile/account is created by admin only after approval/decision |
   | Admin | Provisioned internally only |

2. **Realtime responsibilities (Agora + Ably split)**
   | Capability | Provider |
   |---|---|
   | On-demand voice/video reading | Agora RTC |
   | Live streaming | Agora live streaming |
   | Session text chat realtime | Ably channels (session-scoped) |
   | Presence/online indicators | Ably Presence |
   | Messaging threads | Ably + DB persistence |
   | Community/forum live updates | Ably pub/sub + DB persistence |
   | Typing indicators/read receipts | Ably |
   | Notifications fanout triggers | Worker + Ably (plus push/email) |

3. **Payment compliance (App Store / Play Store)**
   | Purchase type | Web/PWA | Mobile native |
   |---|---|---|
   | Live/private reading services | Stripe | Stripe (service exemption workflow) |
   | Physical products | Stripe | Stripe |
   | Digital products (audio/courses/downloads) | Stripe | Apple/Google IAP (hybrid billing chosen) |
   | Virtual gifts during streams | Stripe web + native platform-compliant flow | Native platform billing where required, mapped to internal gift ledger |

4. **Catalog strategy for Stripe sync + hybrid billing**
   1. Stripe remains the source for service products, physical products, and web digital product pricing.
   2. Internal catalog mirrors Stripe products/prices and adds `platform_billing_channel` metadata (`stripe`, `apple_iap`, `google_play_billing`, `hybrid`).
   3. Digital goods use unified internal entitlement model so purchases from Stripe or IAP unlock the same content.
   4. Admin inventory UI writes via backend to Stripe and updates internal catalog cache; native IAP SKU mapping is managed in the admin catalog screen.

